==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Chromogen
<hw>Chro"mo*gen</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <ety>[Gr. <?/ color +
<ets>-gen</ets>.]</ety> ⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <fld>(Biol.)</fld> <def>Vegetable coloring matter other
than green; chromule.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Chem.)</fld> <def>Any colored compound, supposed to
contain one or more chromophores.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Chromogenic</ent>⟦br⟧
